Fourth Department,

October, 1972

(October 19, 1972) In the Matter of the Probate of the Will of Herman Bauer, Deceased. Ronald S. Cohen, as Executor of Herman Bauer, Deceased, Respondent; Florence S. De Forte, Appellant.

Decree unanimously affirmed, without costs to either party. (See Matter of Kaufmann, 15 N Y 2d 825.) (Appeal from decree of Erie County Surrogate denying probate.) Present — Goldman, P. J., Del Vecchio, Witmer, Cardamone and Henry, JJ.
